==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Snaphance
<hw>Snap"hance`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D.
<ets>snaphaan</ets> a gun, originally, the snapping cock of a gun. See
<er>Snap</er>, and <er>Hen</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A spring lock
for discharging a firearm; also, the firearm to which it is
attached.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A trifling or second-rate thing or person.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Snaphead</ent>⟦br⟧
